    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Drain your<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1584988039205-x200.jpg",
