            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Spread the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> evenly over the top of the pizza base[s] with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong>, <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>and<strong> spicy</strong> <strong>pepper mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
