        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizza[s] is cooking, combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>with your <strong>mayo</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a bowl –<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
